{"tid":2198392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死因存疑的後續...","createTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T17:17:33.000Z","uid":186,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7be968b59c65b09bfe6bbd80ff61949d7a1c975f","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"若未有足夠證據作以上裁斷，陪審團可作「存疑裁決」。一旦如此，<span class=\"red\">家屬可要求警方重新調查</span>，無論警方最終是否展開調查，理論上也應向家屬交代。"},{"pid":"cb0ab43368b57add3f9790b1e56cddc7c3cc986d","tid":2198392,"uid":310127,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"家屬都唔撚care 最後又不了了之。"},{"pid":"45c2cf6d792018f492734c53a1dc5e13f05930c3","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:55.000Z","msg":"本研訊之死因裁斷，將由兩男三女的陪審團決定。按死因庭2019年7月發表的年報，2018年有陪審團的研訊比例達94%。依照法例規定，陪審團須確認死者身份；如何、何時和在何處死亡；對該宗死亡個案的結論。在死因裁判官總結案情後，陪審團可作出的裁斷有以下幾種，包括死於 &mdash; <br />\n<br />\n自然原因，即例如癌症、心臟病等疾病<br />\n倚賴藥物/非倚賴性的濫用藥物，例如是過量使用毒品<br />\n自殺<br />\n意外，即意料之外或偶發的事件導致死亡，例如交通意外或工作時失足<br />\n不幸，即合法行為而導致意料之外的死亡<br />\n合法被殺，例如因警務人員使用槍械自衛或防止他人受傷害而導致死亡<br />\n非法被殺，即死於謀殺或誤殺<br />\n（資料來源為司法機構網頁）<br />\n<br />\n若未有足夠證據作以上裁斷，陪審團可作「存疑裁決」。一旦如此，家屬可要求警方重新調查，無論警方最終是否展開調查，理論上也應向家屬交代。<br />\n<br />\n翻查死因庭年報數據，在2015至2018年間共455宗死因研訊中，有9宗為存疑裁決，只有其中一宗是死因不詳。"},{"pid":"7a47a8086c52b2c06286fdbbe324db31cab92119","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb0ab43368b57add3f9790b1e56cddc7c3cc986d","tid":2198392,"uid":310127,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"家屬都唔撚care 最後又不了了之。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"個阿媽一開始都話唔好再理"},{"pid":"4436bbf88c0d0b1128353bc4a1d418ae57a68db6","tid":2198392,"uid":79410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7a47a8086c52b2c06286fdbbe324db31cab92119","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb0ab43368b57add3f9790b1e56cddc7c3cc986d","tid":2198392,"uid":310127,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"家屬都唔撚care 最後又不了了之。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"個阿媽一開始都話唔好再理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"佢老母極速燒屍. CARE 條撚"},{"pid":"b8dde55bb0e8887c7bfed69f6299ea83ae82d2ff","tid":2198392,"uid":310127,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a47a8086c52b2c06286fdbbe324db31cab92119","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb0ab43368b57add3f9790b1e56cddc7c3cc986d","tid":2198392,"uid":310127,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"家屬都唔撚care 最後又不了了之。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"個阿媽一開始都話唔好再理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"個所謂老母好似由第4日開始都無再旁聽-,-<br />\n今日出黎做埋場戲聽結果就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5cab9a939918e48d19d4a8390658b90be11483","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8dde55bb0e8887c7bfed69f6299ea83ae82d2ff","tid":2198392,"uid":310127,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a47a8086c52b2c06286fdbbe324db31cab92119","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb0ab43368b57add3f9790b1e56cddc7c3cc986d","tid":2198392,"uid":310127,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"家屬都唔撚care 最後又不了了之。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"個阿媽一開始都話唔好再理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"個所謂老母好似由第4日開始都無再旁聽-,-<br />\n今日出黎做埋場戲聽結果就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"得家人可以要求警方調查<br />\n如果有古怪係阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff26a962e7c7301115b4a596486e0ca64d5af48","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"陪審團建議醫管局改善精神科跟進機制，同時建議衞生署考慮日後為遺體進行「矽藻測試」，協助為屍體腐化的死者找出死因。"},{"pid":"ba1e94849448fc30941975b0a87a923fe26f2a86","tid":2198392,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"成件事覺得係：<br />\n順得哥情失嫂意"},{"pid":"f74716a32006f79b244e5660da6ec9b6469b3d18","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"雖然高偉雄提過，陪審團可作出有關防止死亡再發生的建議，而非就調查情況等作出建議。不過高偉雄亦不會阻止，<span class=\"red\">只是不能轉交個別部門跟進。</span><br />\n<br />\n陪審團可作出的裁斷包括死於自然原因、倚賴藥物/非倚賴性的濫用藥物、自殺、意外、不幸、合法被殺及非法被殺。若未有足夠證據作以上裁斷，陪審團可作「存疑裁決」。一旦如此，家屬可要求警方重新調查，無論警方最終是否展開調查，理論上也應向家屬交代。"},{"pid":"c3e4e79c485e526d9c05f55c654e5583ac2cba14","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2121525c55d24e4b4f87dbcce8113938c46e6923","tid":2198392,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"之前的士佬斷頸個單  裁定不合法被殺<br />\n<br />\n咪又係無下文"},{"pid":"180965cb427ed8eaa29f485e234c99a82eb60b25","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431db20093003b2d71d8e59a2d8a332fbbdd55b3","tid":2198392,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"都諗緊會唔會冇下文"},{"pid":"abe6f849aa104d374f8aeb5321367651c1eaf598","tid":2198392,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"